		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've never really seen much info about the SA-1 but I wouldn't be surprised that none of the games really pushed it. From what I've heard it would have been kick ass if more games could have used it, like if it had been included in a CD-ROM system cartridge.

		

		</td>
