	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So the obvious solution for emulating a theoretical-SNESCD would be to add SA-1 + 68k + MIPS R3000. Make it two of each, include the base unit, and it would <em>almost</em> be half as complicated as the Sega Saturn to program for :D

		

		</td>
	</tr>
